sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant UI as Web UI
    participant SC as Smart Contract
    participant PA as Platform Admin

    Note over C,PA: Fase Registrasi
    C->>UI: Connect MetaMask
    UI->>UI: Generate did:key dari wallet address
    UI->>SC: registerDID(did:key)
    SC->>SC: Validasi: wallet belum punya DID
    SC->>SC: Validasi: DID belum diklaim
    SC-->>UI: DID terdaftar on-chain

    Note over C,PA: Fase Verifikasi
    PA->>PA: Verifikasi profil partisipan (off-chain)
    PA->>SC: verifyParticipant(address)
    SC-->>SC: isVerified = true
    PA->>PA: Sign VC (ECDSA secp256k1)
    PA-->>C: Kirim file platform_credential.json

    Note over C,PA: Hasil
    Note right of C: Client memiliki:<br/>1. DID terdaftar on-chain<br/>2. Status isVerified = true<br/>3. File VC bertanda tangan
